---
title: Zesty Hoisin-Chili Beef with Stir-Fry Broccoli and Ginger Rice
description: You'll feel like you've been transported to the streets of Beijing when you taste this fragrant stir-fry. The combination of hoisin sauce, ginger, sweet chili sauce and garlic is a classic combination that adds authentic flavour to the beef and broccoli. Yum!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/zesty-hoisin-chili-beef-88a1b3c4.jpg
